title: Two bedrooms, two baths at an AMAZING price!
posting_body: ['For leasing info, call', 'show contact info', 'today!', 'Ask about ID#: 76128', 'Beautiful architecture and spacious interiors welcome you home to this beautiful community.', 'Our beautifully designed one, two, and three-bedroom apartments for rent in South Austin, TX, are close to St. David’s Hospital, the University of Texas, and the best of Texas hill country.', 'Live in luxury every day with amazing amenities, including a resort-style pool and sundeck, resident clubhouse, game room and lounge, and modern fitness center.', 'Step up to comfort and effortless style at our luxurious apartment community near Southpark Meadows and live the lifestyle you’ve imagined.', 'Apartment amenities include:', 'W/D in unit', 'Granite countertops', 'Plank flooring', 'Stainlesss Steel appliances', 'Kitchen Island', "Don't miss out on this amazing deal.", 'Call me today!', 'Melinda Flemmings, Realtor']
